<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom" xmlns:content="http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/"><channel><title>Iptables on Pan Binghong's Tech Blog</title><link>https://Pan-Binghong.github.io/daily-learning/tags/iptables/</link><description>Recent content in Iptables on Pan Binghong's Tech Blog</description><generator>Hugo -- 0.147.0</generator><language>zh-CN</language><lastBuildDate>Fri, 03 Apr 2026 07:09:15 +0000</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://Pan-Binghong.github.io/daily-learning/tags/iptables/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>Iptables Common commands</title><link>https://Pan-Binghong.github.io/daily-learning/devops/iptables-common-commands/</link><pubDate>Wed, 12 Mar 2025 05:46:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://Pan-Binghong.github.io/daily-learning/devops/iptables-common-commands/</guid><description>&lt;blockquote>
&lt;p>💡 iptables 全称为：netfilter/iptables 是一个IP数据包过滤系统。&lt;/p>&lt;/blockquote>
&lt;hr>
&lt;h2 id="iptables工作流程">iptables工作流程&lt;/h2>
&lt;p>采用数据包过滤机制工作的，所以它会对请求的数据包的包头进行分析，并根据我们预先设定的规则进行匹配来决定是否可以进入主机。&lt;/p>
&lt;ol>
&lt;li>防火墙是一层一层过滤的。实际是按照配置规则的顺序从上到下，从前到后进行filter。&lt;/li>
&lt;li>如果匹配上规则，表明阻止还是通过，此时数据包就不再向下匹配新规则。&lt;/li>
&lt;li>如果规则中，没有表明阻止还是通过，即等同于没有匹配上规则，按照默认策略处理。&lt;/li>
&lt;li>防火墙的默认规则是对应的链的所有规则执行完成后才会执行。
&lt;img loading="lazy" src="https://prod-files-secure.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/fc187c04-cf34-444f-b5f2-bdcdfad76660/5da2e1eb-c9ee-47d7-8b26-5710b6c7fa13/image.png?X-Amz-Algorithm=AWS4-HMAC-SHA256&amp;X-Amz-Content-Sha256=UNSIGNED-PAYLOAD&amp;X-Amz-Credential=ASIAZI2LB4664A4PAC5P%2F20260403%2Fus-west-2%2Fs3%2Faws4_request&amp;X-Amz-Date=20260403T070822Z&amp;X-Amz-Expires=3600&amp;X-Amz-Security-Token=IQoJb3JpZ2luX2VjELb%2F%2F%2F%2F%2F%2F%2F%2F%2F%2FwEaCXVzLXdlc3QtMiJGMEQCIDe8oWhJNxkS1PXoUMcMFNeUUhjoCdSBdUMaF6nqbHIGAiBWVLiEoINuA9dFVj7lR5sGYM7EQ8cn491B5gHOPctXIir%2FAwh%2FEAAaDDYzNzQyMzE4MzgwNSIMgv%2Fr4zAoiGIEr0iSKtwDdbmafgmjhqd8j4AiVFPatXt3QIELM5AMynr5v3Yt%2BgR85i4zoYVnPHTFj20Rdpp7pKWT3QwdDh1aHyWInJKK2ZWlJgz2chygifDt7kuUC7ACqkDmvAmBzwF2k%2FjhkLlYvsvVYT27awjQjaUXrTG4imsUUpSLeBm5X8LZRAiALb0nArPlGK1b38yPYO1PsSSi%2BEuxydJNVSqpfASuD60Hznl5ozyrWhjb88%2BWQifrfmYgd9%2FKY4nR79gG2%2BnJ5J3l2nugsa1BVi3JFk2rV%2Bho0i9vpVYJuDatO57UQNGpX12GxV%2BnJ5OgXKGK4MbqknBND%2FXS%2Bzp3oQrkEtcurgHhGiJQTKUp%2BcBqwkDwJ3y148LZ0add2V6w1fgpZtlaRPoZckB7xWgd%2Fywq0AlFS%2B1eRyXAnzntAZ6ELDy5DXz71XpLgoXaV4b5Fc7msqt1cq4LvIAJ5D9mHr3%2FsufxqsUZ%2B4bbLf1DpjwQnZmO%2B417r8uGiVkfjrk0eYiNMLDYPy7pUeFqGdktHAY3EyGqGBGn%2FgntQYQAKAd0bmBi8%2B7nN0wzNle4o51hGUS7Cc953t2mx%2FObCGFmvf1AEpVEifHtksITNrxFhbvQS7b17deUC23zIdxC3XghBaz3HBUw3qu9zgY6pgH31Ci%2F9ASCOx9GovtLpGPzFzWbgESP8XP%2BpB9JgcAbaH8Jg4mwI9VNg0rvUebMOgFjrCFoA9%2F38F%2FqVYVIFxaDjlfB%2F%2Fw41GR3kVUfYSLj2wAxVnd7Y6ekybzXZwm2ijwFVGVgptBSu3%2FDvNt4RS6aOiwrvF7cvglxHiAJvVuBjVsy6I9ucrRDd7clmimfDKs3ZloEqNqSXEXmC9ZImo4BJ%2B3ZpgDh&amp;X-Amz-Signature=6fbbd1b446a179c3e2fcbbc25fc6d9ed74fdd60e658d8b21e8f8a77985b96e08&amp;X-Amz-SignedHeaders=host&amp;x-amz-checksum-mode=ENABLED&amp;x-id=GetObject">&lt;/li>
&lt;/ol>
